<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>邀請卡與信封線上文字提案編輯器 (客戶專用)</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        
        /* 浮水印背景特效 */
        .watermark-bg {
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6f4ea 0%, #f4fbf7 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .watermark-bg::before {
            content: "活動主視覺";
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-15deg);
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(74, 161, 98, 0.08);
            white-space: nowrap;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
            letter-spacing: 0.5rem;
        }

        .watermark-bg-pink {
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeef2 0%, #fff7f9 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .watermark-bg-pink::before {
            content: "活動主視覺";
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-15deg);
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.07);
            white-space: nowrap;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
            letter-spacing: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* 虛擬折線 */
        .fold-line {
            position: relative;
        }
        .fold-line::after {
            content: "【折線】";
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 11px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            border: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        /* 輸入框樣式優化 */
        .editable-input {
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: 1px dashed transparent;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .editable-input:hover {
            border-color: #10b981;
            background-color: rgba(230, 244, 234, 0.7);
        }
        .editable-input:focus {
            border-color: #059669;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            border-style: solid;
        }

        .editable-input-pink:hover {
            border-color: #ec4899;
            background-color: rgba(254, 242, 242, 0.7);
        }
        .editable-input-pink:focus {
            border-color: #db2777;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.2);
            border-style: solid;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen text-gray-800 flex flex-col">

    <!-- 頂部導覽列 -->
    <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-700 text-white shadow-lg sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-white text-emerald-600 p-2 rounded-lg font-black text-xl shadow-inner">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-file-signature"></i> CARD
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-wider">邀請卡客戶線上文字確認提案系統</h1>
                    <p class="text-xs text-emerald-100">快速填寫、即時預覽、一鍵定稿匯出</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex gap-2">
                <button onclick="loadTemplate('default')" class="bg-emerald-800 hover:bg-emerald-900 text-white text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded transition flex items-center gap-1.5">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i> 重設預設範例 (水梨節)
                </button>
                <button onclick="clearAllFields()" class="bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-700 text-white text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded transition flex items-center gap-1.5">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-eraser"></i> 清空文字
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- 操作提示說明 -->
    <div class="bg-emerald-50 border-b border-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-3">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-emerald-500 text-white w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">!</span>
            <div>
                <p class="font-semibold">親愛的客戶您好：</p>
                <p class="text-emerald-700 mt-0.5">
                    以下卡片的所有<b>文字與長官名單、記者會時間表</b>均為「可編輯輸入框」。您可直接在想要修改的字體上點選並輸入您真正的活動資訊。
                    底圖的所有精美背景與插畫區塊在設計階段已用<b>【活動主視覺】浮水印</b>佔位替代。文字定案後，我們將為您套入正式主視覺。
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 分頁導覽按鈕 & 匯出動作列 -->
    <div class="sticky top-[72px] bg-white border-b border-gray-200 shadow-sm z-40 py-2">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
            <!-- Tabs -->
            <div class="flex bg-gray-100 p-1.5 rounded-xl w-full md:w-auto overflow-x-auto">
                <button onclick="switchTab('tab-outer')" id="btn-tab-outer" class="tab-btn flex-1 md:flex-none text-sm font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-emerald-700 shadow-sm">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-map"></i> 1. 邀請卡 - 外頁 (封面/封底)
                </button>
                <button onclick="switchTab('tab-inner')" id="btn-tab-inner" class="tab-btn flex-1 md:flex-none text-sm font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-emerald-600">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-book-open"></i> 2. 邀請卡 - 內頁 (致邀內容/流程)
                </button>
                <button onclick="switchTab('tab-envelope')" id="btn-tab-envelope" class="tab-btn flex-1 md:flex-none text-sm font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-emerald-600">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> 3. 粉紅色信封套 (郵寄版面)
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Export Buttons -->
            <div class="flex gap-2 w-full md:w-auto">
                <button onclick="exportData()" class="flex-1 md:flex-none bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg shadow transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i> 一鍵定稿 (複製文字/匯出)
                </button>
                <button onclick="window.print();" class="bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white font-bold px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg shadow transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-print"></i> 列印 / 存成PDF
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 主要編輯區域 -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-6xl w-full mx-auto p-4 md:p-8">
        
        <!-- ==================== TAB 1: 外頁 ==================== -->
        <div id="tab-outer" class="tab-content block">
            <div class="mb-6 text-center">
                <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">邀請卡外頁 (長卡對折 - 上下對折)</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">上方為倒立摺回來的封面，中間為折線，下方為展開後的封底。</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="max-w-[550px] mx-auto bg-white border border-gray-300 shadow-2xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                <!-- 邀請卡外頁上半部 (封面折疊頁 - 在平面展示時為倒置 180度 以便對折後呈現正面) -->
                <div class="watermark-bg border-b border-gray-200 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[380px] transform rotate-180 select-none relative">
                    <!-- 上半部頂端 (折疊後在底層) -->
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <input type="text" id="outer-back-title" value="誠 摯 邀 請 INVITATION" class="editable-input text-center text-pink-600 font-black text-2xl tracking-widest bg-transparent w-full pointer-events-auto">
                    </div>

                    <!-- 封面大主題 (主視覺浮水印中) -->
                    <div class="my-auto text-center py-4">
                        <div class="inline-block bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm px-6 py-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm pointer-events-auto w-full">
                            <input type="text" id="outer-main-title" value="甘甜蜜意豐貓梨" class="editable-input text-center text-emerald-800 font-extrabold text-3xl tracking-widest bg-transparent w-full">
                            <input type="text" id="outer-sub-title" value="2025苗栗水果節" class="editable-input text-center text-emerald-600 font-bold text-lg tracking-wider bg-transparent w-full mt-2">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 上半部插畫佔位區 -->
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">
                        <div class="border border-dashed border-gray-300 p-1 rounded bg-white/60">[活動主視覺插畫佔位 A]</div>
                        <div class="border border-dashed border-gray-300 p-1 rounded bg-white/60">[活動主視覺插畫佔位 B]</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 虛擬折線 -->
                <div class="fold-line h-px border-t-2 border-dashed border-gray-400 my-0 bg-gray-100 py-3"></div>

                <!-- 邀請卡外頁下半部 (封底 / 指導主協辦單位) -->
                <div class="watermark-bg p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[380px]">
                    <!-- 中間大片主視覺示意區 -->
                    <div class="my-auto flex flex-col items-center justify-center border-2 border-dashed border-emerald-200/50 rounded-2xl p-6 bg-white/40 min-h-[160px] text-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-leaf text-emerald-500 text-3xl mb-2"></i>
                        <span class="text-emerald-800 font-bold text-lg">【此處將呈現：正式活動主視覺插圖】</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1">(包含豐水梨主體、採梨農夫、滿滿的苗栗果園溫馨氛圍)</span>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 封底最下方的單位資料區 -->
                    <div class="mt-8 space-y-2 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100 text-sm">
                        <div class="flex">
                            <span class="font-bold text-emerald-700 w-24 flex-shrink-0">指導單位：</span>
                            <input type="text" id="outer-guide-org" value="苗栗縣政府、苗栗縣三灣鄉公所" class="editable-input text-gray-700 bg-transparent w-full">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex">
                            <span class="font-bold text-emerald-700 w-24 flex-shrink-0">主辦單位：</span>
                            <input type="text" id="outer-main-org" value="三灣鄉農會" class="editable-input text-gray-700 bg-transparent w-full">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex">
                            <span class="font-bold text-emerald-700 w-24 flex-shrink-0">協辦單位：</span>
                            <input type="text" id="outer-co-org" value="三灣鄉民代表會、鄉內各機關團體" class="editable-input text-gray-700 bg-transparent w-full">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex">
                            <span class="font-bold text-emerald-700 w-24 flex-shrink-0">廣告標註：</span>
                            <input type="text" id="outer-ad-tag" value="廣告" class="editable-input text-gray-400 text-xs bg-transparent w-full">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ==================== TAB 2: 內頁 ==================== -->
        <div id="tab-inner" class="tab-content hidden">
            <div class="mb-6 text-center">
                <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">邀請卡內頁 (對開展開面)</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">上方為長官致邀內容，中間為折線，下方為記者會活動流程安排。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-[550px] mx-auto bg-white border border-gray-300 shadow-2xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                <!-- 內頁上半部 (致邀主旨/時間地點/長官名單) -->
                <div class="watermark-bg p-8 border-b border-gray-200 min-h-[460px] flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <!-- 致邀主文 -->
                    <div class="text-center space-y-3 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100">
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-emerald-700 font-bold mb-1">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-day"></i>
                            <input type="text" id="inner-invitation-head" value="謹訂於民國114年7月22日（二）上午10點" class="editable-input text-center text-sm font-bold bg-transparent w-full">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-emerald-700 font-bold">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                            <input type="text" id="inner-invitation-loc" value="假 苗栗縣政府大廳 舉辦" class="editable-input text-center text-sm font-bold bg-transparent w-full">
                        </div>
                        <div class="pt-2 border-t border-dashed border-emerald-100">
                            <input type="text" id="inner-event-name-1" value="114年度苗栗縣豐水梨果品評鑑競賽頒獎暨行銷活動" class="editable-input text-center text-emerald-900 font-black text-md bg-transparent w-full">
                            <input type="text" id="inner-event-name-2" value="2025苗栗水果節 甘甜蜜意豐貓梨" class="editable-input text-center text-emerald-700 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full mt-1">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-pink-600 font-bold text-sm tracking-widest pt-1">
                            <input type="text" id="inner-welcome-tag" value="敬祈撥冗 蒞臨指導" class="editable-input text-center bg-transparent w-full">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 長官敬邀聯名名單 (動態卡片) -->
                    <div class="mt-6 bg-white/85 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100 text-xs">
                        <!-- 動態網格容器 -->
                        <div id="officers-container" class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
                            <!-- 預設長官資料項目，職稱與姓名均改為 input -->
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="苗栗縣縣長" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="鍾東錦" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="三灣鄉鄉長" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="李運光" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="立法委員" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="邱鎮軍" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="三灣鄉農會理事長" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="賴元鳳" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="苗栗縣議會議長" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="李文斌" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="三灣鄉農會常務監事" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="廖盛榮" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="三灣鄉民代表會主席" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="邱騰森" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-dashed border-emerald-100/50 pb-1 officer-item">
                                <input type="text" value="三灣鄉農會總幹事" class="editable-input text-emerald-800 font-medium text-xs bg-transparent w-24 flex-shrink-0 outline-none">
                                <input type="text" value="謝杏玲" class="editable-input text-blue-800 font-bold text-sm bg-transparent w-full outline-none">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 增刪長官名單按鈕 (僅在非列印狀態顯示) -->
                        <div class="mt-3 flex justify-end gap-1.5 no-print">
                            <button onclick="addOfficer()" class="bg-emerald-100 hover:bg-emerald-200 text-emerald-800 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded transition flex items-center gap-1">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i> ➕ 新增長官
                            </button>
                            <button onclick="removeOfficer()" class="bg-rose-100 hover:bg-rose-200 text-rose-800 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded transition flex items-center gap-1">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-minus"></i> ➖ 刪除最後一位
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 敬邀按鈕樣式 -->
                        <div class="flex justify-center mt-3 pt-2 border-t border-emerald-50">
                            <span class="bg-pink-600 text-white rounded-full font-bold px-4 py-1 text-xs shadow-sm tracking-widest">
                                <input type="text" id="inner-invite-badge" value="敬邀" class="text-center bg-transparent w-12 text-white font-bold outline-none">
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 虛擬折線 -->
                <div class="fold-line h-px border-t-2 border-dashed border-gray-400 my-0 bg-gray-100 py-3"></div>

                <!-- 內頁下半部 (流程時間表) -->
                <div class="watermark-bg p-6 md:p-8 min-h-[460px] flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100">
                        <div class="text-emerald-800 font-bold text-md mb-3 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-emerald-100 pb-2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i>
                            <input type="text" id="inner-flow-title" value="記者會流程" class="editable-input font-bold text-emerald-800 bg-transparent w-40">
                        </div>

                        <!-- 流程圖表 -->
                        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-emerald-100">
                            <table class="w-full text-center text-xs">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr class="bg-teal-600 text-white font-semibold">
                                        <th class="py-2.5 w-1/3 border-r border-teal-500">時間</th>
                                        <th class="py-2.5 w-2/3">單元</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody id="flow-tbody" class="divide-y divide-emerald-50">
                                    <tr class="hover:bg-emerald-50/50 bg-amber-50/50 transition">
                                        <td class="py-2 px-2 border-r border-emerald-50"><input type="text" value="10:00-10:02" class="editable-input text-center w-full bg-transparent"></td>
                                        <td class="py-2 px-2"><input type="text" value="主持人開場" class="editable-input text-center font-medium w-full bg-transparent"></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="hover:bg-emerald-50/50 transition">
                                        <td class="py-2 px-2 border-r border-emerald-50"><input type="text" value="10:02-10:07" class="editable-input text-center w-full bg-transparent"></td>
                                        <td class="py-2 px-2"><input type="text" value="開場表演" class="editable-input text-center font-medium w-full bg-transparent"></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="hover:bg-emerald-50/50 bg-amber-50/50 transition">
                                        <td class="py-2 px-2 border-r border-emerald-50"><input type="text" value="10:07-10:12" class="editable-input text-center w-full bg-transparent"></td>
